title: Mike Vecchione: Florida Class
description:
Kippy and Foley are back with a classic episode with the hilarious Mike Vecchione. Mike talks growing up in Florida, wrestling, and Youngstown Ohio. You know Mike from No Disrespect Podcast, Comedy Central, Tonight Show, and the King of Staten Island.
